# Insulin Degludec

## Overview

Ultra-long-acting basal insulin analog forming multi-hexamer chains for very prolonged glucose lowering.

## Structure

| Property | Value |
| -------- | ----- |
| Name     | Insulin Degludec |

## Mechanism of Action

Hexadecanedioic acid at Lys-B29 enables fatty acid acylation; subcutaneous precipitation and albumin binding create ultra-long duration exceeding 42 hours.

